<h3>Service <code>climate.turn_on</code></h3>
<p>Turn climate device on. This is only supported if the climate device supports being turned off.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Service data attribute</th>
<th>Optional</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>entity_id</code></td>
<td>yes</td>
<td>String or list of strings that define the entity ID(s) of climate device(s) to control. To target all climate devices, use <code>all</code>.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>Service <code>climate.turn_off</code></h3>
<p>Turn climate device off. This is only supported if the climate device has the hvac mode <code>off</code>.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Service data attribute</th>
<th>Optional</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>entity_id</code></td>
<td>yes</td>
<td>String or list of strings that define the entity ID(s) of climate device(s) to control. To target all climate devices, use <code>all</code>.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
